######
Download Genome Seq from Ensembl
ensembl ftp :  https://useast.ensembl.org/info/data/ftp/index.html
Choose Human FASTA and GFF3

After download, run ubuntu bash to unzip.
gunzip *.gz

cd ~/STAR/bin/Linum_x86_64
STAR --runMode genomeGenerate --runThreadN 8 --genomeDir /mnt/e/RNAData/GRCh38.91STARIndex/ -- genomeFastaFiles /mnt/e/RNAData/GRCh38.91STARIndex/Home_sapiens.GRCh38.dna.primary_assembly.fa --sjdbGTFfile /mnt/e/RNAData/GRCh38.91STARIndex/Home_sapiens.GRCh38.91.gff3

######
Aother software for RNA-Seq De novo Assembly is Trinity.

######
Cufflinks use UCSC GTF/GFF3 gene annotation. STAR use Ensemble GTF/GFF3 annotation. After mapping, a transfer is needed by ChromosomeMapping/GRCh38_ensembl2UCSC.txt

